import React, { Component } from "react";

class MenuBar extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <header className="fixed-top">
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="lg" sticky="top" id="sidebar">
          <Container fluid style={{ marginLeft: 40, marginRight: 40 }}>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Logo</Navbar.Brand>

            <Navbar.Collapse id="sidebar" className="justify-content-end">
              <Nav
                onSelect={() =>
                  this.setState({
                    navExpanded: false,
                  })
                }
                defaultActiveKey="#home"
              >
                <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="#link">Link</Nav.Link>
                <NavDropdown title="Dropdown" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                  <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Action</NavDropdown.Item>
                  <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">
                    Another action
                  </NavDropdown.Item>
                  <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">
                    Something
                  </NavDropdown.Item>
                  <NavDropdown.Divider />
                  <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">
                    Separated link
                  </NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
                <Button variant="primary" onClick={() => this.handleShow()}>
                  Register/Login
                </Button>
              </Nav>
            </Navbar.Collapse>
            <Modal show={this.state.setShow} onHide={() => this.handleClose()}>
              <Modal.Header closeButton>
                <Modal.Title>Registration Page</Modal.Title>
              </Modal.Header>
              <Modal.Body>
                {this.state.registered == false
                  ? this.registerPage()
                  : this.loginPage()}
              </Modal.Body>
            </Modal>
          </Container>
        </Navbar>
      </header>
    );
  }
}

export default MenuBar;
